Summary: starlike bright red / green flashing motionless for 30 minutes
divs: Sighting DetailsNoticed unusual star-like flashing object, motionless, it was moonless nite, we see stars a lot here, never seen this...it stayed there for maybe 30 mins, I looked at it thru binoculars, then went to get telescope, tried to lock on it, then it headed west and 2 fast jets headed diectly toward it from Milwaukee and it was gone. This object was high in the sky about 5-10 miles northwest of East Troy Wisconsin.
